    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Talking About Race</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>James C Leong letter questions why views of Asians were left out of July 16 issue on race in America0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Mexicans making sushi; a redheaded white boy joining a Chinese gang and shooting up a bank; Asian sex kittens with their white boyfriends. No wonder we Asians were summarily excluded from President Clinton's Dialogue on Race. Why weren't we allowed our voice in your issue on race? We also have kitchens and living rooms, and we do speakee English.</p>
        <p>James C. Leong  Seattle</p>
      </block>
